To Install LXDE
Make sure you are on base with no desktop environment
1 sudo pacman -S lxde lxdm; sudo systemctl enable lxdm; sudo systemctl start lxdm
2 For KDE Plasma Users Run sudo pacman -Rns plasma-meta then sudo pacman -Rns dolphin then sudo pacman -Rns plasma-workspace sudo pacman -Rns kate
3 Go To Desktop Preferences Then Change Wallpaper lxde-blue.jpg To Frozenworld Or Frozenworld (Compile It)
